  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Operation Manager",
  "description": "<h3><strong>The Role</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a hands-on leader to run our café. You will lead the team, manage the floor, and ensure every customer leaves happy.</p><h3><strong>What You Will Do</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Run Operations:</strong> Manage daily shifts for both Front of House and Kitchen.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lead the Team:</strong> Train staff, plan rosters, and motivate the crew.</p></li><li><p><strong>Quality Control:</strong> Ensure food quality and service standards are always high.</p></li><li><p><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Handle feedback and resolve issues professionally.</p></li><li><p><strong>Admin & Hygiene:</strong> Manage inventory/ordering, daily reports, and ensure strict NEA/SFA hygiene compliance.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Need</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Experience:</strong> At least <strong>1 years</strong> managing a café or F&B outlet.</p></li><li><p><strong>Availability:</strong> Able to work <strong>6 days a week</strong>, including weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p><strong>Skills:</strong> Strong leadership, organized, and willing to get your hands dirty. Barista skills are a big plus!</p></li></ul>",
